1. USING HTML

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>Weather App</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Weather App</h1>
        <div id="weather-info">
            <p>Loading...</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

2. USING CSS
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
